### Description

Hi

I have made a fluent api for form builder.
Especially because the addControl method does not return the FormGroup

### Proposed solution

https://gist.github.com/wokier/46ddb0aa49ddf104b456e0f1e90a99bf
Usage
```
return this.fbc.group({
      origine: [data?.origine],
      destination: [data?.destination : null],
    }).add('another', this.manuallyCreatedController, data.another)
      .add('yetanother', this.alsoManuallyCreatedController.selectedCtrl, data?.yetanother)
      .build();
```

### Alternatives considered

```
FormGroup formGroup = this.fb.group({
      origine: [data?.origine],
      destination: [data?.destination : null],
    });
formGroup.add('another', this.manuallyCretedController, data.another);
formGroup.add('yetanother', this.alsoManuallyCretedController.selectedCtrl, data?.yetanother);
return formGroup;
```

